					<![CDATA[
						 <p>ever since Randomini introduced her, we've seen Iris Dark a lot. I decided to focus on the Old Dark. inspired by a conversation <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3938622&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1555119399" alt="The Great Hippo" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3938622)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" >The Great Hippo</a></span> was having with <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gabriel-jade" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=414239&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1555119399" alt="Gabriel Jade" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=414239)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gabriel-jade" >Gabriel Jade</a></span> on irc that ended up going in a different direction to this concept but i would feel weird not crediting the inspiration. title is from Party Out of Bounds by the B52s. Roger Waters wrote &quot;Money&quot;, I assume a single line as an homage is fair use.</p> <p>Crit credits:</p> <ul> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1581620&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1555119399" alt="DarkStuff" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1581620)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" >DarkStuff</a></span> - <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4467">SCP-4467</a> &quot;Oh, I Get It Now&quot;</li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greenwolf" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1814684&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1555119399" alt="GreenWolf" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1814684)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greenwolf" >GreenWolf</a></span> - <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/minneapolis-burns">Minneapolis Burns</a></li> <li><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2038009&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1555119399" alt="TyGently" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2038009)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" >TyGently</a></span> - <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/a-confluence-of-clandestine-conferences">A Confluence of Clandestine Conferences</a></li> </ul> 
